Package pl.put.poznan.sorting.rest

package pl.put.poznan.sorting.rest
The rest package contains the RESTful web services for the Sorting Madness application. It includes the controller that handles HTTP requests and interacts with the core sorting logic.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    SortingMadnessController
    The SortingMadnessController class is a REST controller that handles HTTP requests for sorting operations using various algorithms.
